<p><a href="/7523/0205/1/en">Money, energy, human labor</a></p>
<p>
Money - is an analogue of energy. The energy required to produce a product (good or service). In fact, Marx wrote about the same thing - only needed for the production of human labor. Human labor - that is, this energy - this is real money!
